														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4539462">
									

<p>I didn't find this piece scary, and I don't get how it fits the theme besides the C4 being mentioned. I think it suffers from how underexplained the premise is. The file might do something really freaky, or it could just be a malware shutting down computers for someone's lolz. Many creepy stories operate with a similar trope, but usually they make a good job on making you <em>want</em> the monster to be safe, but understand somewhere deep that it's really not. This piece didn't do it, and I find it ineffective.</p>

							</div>

								
					
