			<div class="content" id="post-content-4539624">
									

<p>It kinda feel a bit too comical to the overall tone of Parawatch. I guess the GoI is supposed to be a bunch of internet rando but like, there's no real rhyme or reason hereasto why these people got the file in their computer.</p>
<p>also, if we're talking about the same *.rdp that is remote desktop protocol config file, then triskade-something is pulling shit outta their ass. it's definitely capable of remotely accessing the computers, not just simple commands. it's <em>most likely</em> not the form of stuff that electronic people would use, or at least not one they would use in remote controls&#8212;it's the equivalent of lifting an entire house to move a desk. remotes won't even generate files at all, it'll generate <em>packets</em> maybe, perhaps IP/TCP on fancier stuff like Drone remotes.</p>

