			<div class="content" id="post-content-4541239">
									

<p>Hoo boy. Gonna talk through my feelings here.</p>
<p>I might be the minority, but I thought you were perfectly understated in your ending. Computer go boom. I thought that was actually brilliant.</p>
<p>Had to go read through some other Parawatch things to figure out if it fit the GoI, and I think it does in the &quot;there is no canon&quot; and &quot;seriously the internet is like this&quot; sort of ways.</p>
<p>So yeah I think that's a +1.</p>

