														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4551143">
									

<p>The conclusion of this was wholly unsatisfying. The computer blew up, and that's it. With the correct buildup, this could have been an effective anticlimax, but all this consisted of was a few overused jokes about deleting files, and that one C4 section which all but physically hit me with the meaning behind the ending. I get that it was an attempt to create some form of clue or hint, but it was far too obvious and narratively convenient.</p>

